ce:section.ce:para:
Supplementary Fig. S5 compares the streaming velocities from our current work with available theoretical predictions. The markers in green indicate the streaming velocity values obtained circumferentially around bubble (

      θ

) from our simulation. The values from our PIV experiment are shown by yellow triangles. The deviation noted may be attributed to the eulerian streaming velocity and the lagrangian streaming velocity captured respectively from theoretical studies and particle tracer experiments, this was also observed by Wu and Du [19].
